resources.string:
1.Goods: The company add items that are sent to each store through the sales template; 
2. Mobile collection: By default, payment in each store is collected by the company and the company needs to open an account. The store can also set up separate money collection; 
3. Member: Member level, top-up rules, etc. are created by the company. All stores execute these setups accordingly; 
4. Report: The company can see reports of all stores.
